'''雅莉安娜·坦莉雅·蘇迪·米蘭達'''（Ariadna Thalia Sodi Miranda，{{IPA-es|aɾiˈaðna taˈli.a ˈsoði miˈɾanda}}，{{bd|1971年|8月26日}}），一般稱作'''坦莉雅'''，是墨西哥歌手、作家、演員及企業家，其演唱語言包括西語、英語、葡語及菲律賓語<ref name="Billboard 1997">{{cite news|url=http://books.google.com.gt/books?id=oxMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA30&dq=Thal%C3%ADa+to+release+Arrasando&hl=es&sa=X&ei=O8qaT4yuGOK02gXws9mNDw&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Thal%C3%ADa%20to%20release%20Arrasando&f=false|title=THE BILLBOARD STAR AWARD : Thalía | The Mexican Singer/Actress Has Risen From Kiddie Pop To Soap Operas To International Status|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher=[[Google_Books|Google Books]]|date=March 2011|accessdate=August 11, 2012|language=|archive-date=2015-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150102121026/http://books.google.com.gt/books?id=oxMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA30&dq=Thal%C3%ADa+to+release+Arrasando&hl=es&sa=X&ei=O8qaT4yuGOK02gXws9mNDw&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Thal%C3%ADa%20to%20release%20Arrasando&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。坦莉雅公認是墨西哥最成功及最具影響力的女歌手<ref name="Billboard2014">{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6312343/thalia-on-amore-mio-album-macys-clothing-line-tommy-mottola|title=Latin Pop Queen Thalia on Her New Album 'Amore Mio': 'I've Started a Brand-New Career, With No Ties or Taboos'|work=Billboard|date=November 2014|accessdate=2015-02-09|quote=Up to now, the ultimate diva and most influential Mexican singer.|archive-date=2015-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120095927/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6312343/thalia-on-amore-mio-album-macys-clothing-line-tommy-mottola|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Oye">{{cite news|url=http://www.oyemexico.com/nota/25-mexicanos-mas-influyentes-en-la-musica/|title=25 mexicanos más influyentes en la música|work=Oyemexico.com|date=|accessdate=August 10, 2012|language=es|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121208213808/http://www.oyemexico.com/nota/25-mexicanos-mas-influyentes-en-la-musica/|archive-date=2012-12-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Televisa">{{cite news|url=http://especiales.televisa.com/musica/noticias/512948/thalia-con-nuevo-disco/|title=Thalía con nuevo disco|work=[[Televisa|Televisa]]|date=|accessdate=August 27, 2012|language=es|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054233/http://especiales.televisa.com/musica/noticias/512948/thalia-con-nuevo-disco/|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="TV Azteca">{{cite news|url=http://www.azteca.com/notas/vengalaalegria/128322/thalia-una-de-las-mexicanas-mas-tocadas|title=Ellas son las mexicanas más tocadas|work=[[Azteca_(multimedia_company)|Azteca]]|author=Ana Karen Grande Benavides|date=August 30, 2012|accessdate=August 10, 2012|language=es|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029194540/http://www.azteca.com/notas/vengalaalegria/128322/thalia-una-de-las-mexicanas-mas-tocadas|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref> ，是墨西哥紅極一時的天后，國際媒體稱她為「拉丁流行天后」。

